        <div class="component-content">
<h2>Overview</h2>
<p>Retail today covers everything from supermarkets to luxury stores; from buying shoes on Instagram to telling Alexa to order shampoo. They are all different, but they all have one thing in common: converting brands into sales. The omnichannel consumer landscape requires a deep understanding of shoppers, retailers, channels and ecosystems &ndash; and we can help.</p>        </div>
